cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on the evaluation of deformable face tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of different architectures and strategies, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the evaluation of tracking performance could also be relevant to cs.RO (Robotics).
